msgid ""
"Before proceeding with the installation, we need to disable the Windows "
"mechanism that allows only signed drivers to be installed, because "
"currently, the drivers provided as part of the Windows Tools are not "
"digitally signed with a publicly recognizable certificate. To do that:"
